Well i havent wrote in this thing since a year ago...but I just wanted to say a year really does make a difference looking back wow..and..all that Brandon drama was so stupid and i cant believe i wasted my time. I guess i learned from it. Now im not saying hes out of my life bc IT NEVER STOPS..but i have a love of my life now his name is Josh hes so wonderful everything I ever wanted. So all that waiting i finally found what i was looking for. I really dont have drama much anymore i quit cheerleading. i can finally say im moving on..in a lot of things and im a better person for it. Im growing up Im going to college next year and i think im the happiest I ever been. Of course ppl have come and gone. But everything is a lesson..and the story of my life keeps going. I never thought i would be in the place i am now..I still have so much to learn. 

I guess growing up isnt too bad even though i cried my eyes out yesterday bc i didnt want to grow up. But looking back it isnt too bad. lol

Peace out

Well.....nothing is really going. Everything is okay for the time being. Tiff has called shes fine, which is good.

My friend isnt mad at me anymore :-D

Everything is okay. 

Ive been watching movies to cure my boredness. Last nite my mom and dad actually let me leave. I picked up Steph and Mary. We were gonna watch movies but blockbusters wasnt open. So we decided to find somewhere to eat and we ended up going to chickfila went back to stephs to eat it. THen Leo finally called and we hang out with him for a lil while. We had bunch of fun! I love them they are awesome. We were so hott we had country music on and up loud all of singing lol. We are dorkous! It was great, I was happy to get out of the house before the hurricane. 

Today I went to blockbuster dropped off two movies and came home watched movies. Lol so basically im being a huge bum!

Last nite I found so many old memories. There was only one thing i regret doing..I regreted so much late nite. I wish I never had done what I did. THen today I realize EVERYTHING HAPPENS FOR A REASON. I have my whole life to live...mistakes are for learning..and life moves on!

I gonna quit being such a drama queen but you know I love it. 
I was so unhappy, but now I look around and its so much crap. I have it all..and I know what I want in life. So Im gonna work to get it. Nothing is going to stop me.

People come and go in my life, but the people that stay make it worth wild. 

I love everyone thats in my life, and Im so grateful! 

Its time to move on...

Ive found it easier if I just leave it alone, it will all come together. Thats what Im going to do.

the end..

be safe everyone love yous!

oxox

All day today I was freaking out about the hurricane, not for orlando but for PSL. Tiff lives there, Im so frickin scared for her. I know she will be fine thou. 

Also Him, I want him right next to me. I know what it is. Hes been my security blanket for so long, and now Im so use to him being there. I miss when hes not. Of course he wasnt there for a year and a half..but..thats a different story. Im glad I told him everything last nite. In case something happens at least he knows!

I feel like a 2 year old so hopeless. All day everyone around me has been panicing..I just want to cry thats..all just cry.

When he called last nite, he knew right away that I was crying, I tried to play it off that im just sick, which I am, but I was also crying. He came..he was here in 5 mins. {right when I give up on him, hes pulls through EVERYTIME!}

He cares..but we both need that security that neither of us hold.. thats the problem we both ask questions soo much about each other we are both scared of the hurt. "Where did you sick from?" He asks like I was with someone else.."Um..well my dad is sick, so probably him"

Especially me, him im not sure about..hes scared he doesnt want to get into another commitment which DUH..he just got over this huge thing..so of course thats understandable. I think he didnt know my feelings {well he wasnt sure of them} cuz i would play it off like i didnt want a bf cuz i didnt, then after awhile..it was a lie..i couldnt lie anymore. I had to tell him..I had feelings, that it wasnt all fun and games. Keeping it from him HURT soo much! I was scared he would see right through me, which he did, but of course i played it off. Covered well! 

I know all this, I know all possibilities, so naturally im scared to death. I know one of us will get hurt in the end. Like last time, but he was the one left hurt and it was my fault.{and i hated myself for it!} So it would be my turn. 

He knows I care but he doesnt know..what really is going on..no one really does. 

I want to just be friends. I do not want to loose him. I cant loose him. when i lost him for that year and a half..i hated it..i missed him so much. 

But then i want him here, with me more then just a friend.

I dont care what anyone says..if youve done something with someone {kissing} and youve had a past..it brings up feelings..

Last nite I couldnt even frickin say it to his face, but he knew..He asked "So whats wrong?" "Would you rather text me?" "Actually dont tell me, just go get the note." He knew I couldnt/wouldnt tell him. I couldnt even speak. I wasnt crying cuz of him thou, there is so much more..lol {other things going on..} He made me smile thou.

When he called after he left I felt better, it was like he resured me again. 

Somewhere I know Im looking too far into this..

I want to be friends with him I cant loose him, but none of this I can control its totally in his hands...

For once..after all my screwing up..all the messing up I did in the past. This is in his hands. I cant and will not do anything more. He will come to me..he knows the number he knows where i live. Hes know how I feel, but I will not wait.

now for the hurricane Im scared to death for all my friends but im more at ease cuz my mom just came in and said it is dying down! So maybe ill sleep and get over thinking that my friends and family are going to die and that i will die if anything happens to them..

I saw him twice, once at his work and he came over. I gave him the note. He called after he read it, he didnt have a responds to it, SO idk? but i feel better knowing he knows the WHOLe truth even why i broke up with him in the first place and how I still have feelings..

So either good move or bad move. Idc. im just glad its out it was killing me!!!! Either way i win. either i get to be with him or we are just friends and nothing more. either way ill be happy as a clown! 

He made me feel better, thou, I missed him!

woot btw the game was cancled WOOT!!!!!!!!!!! *doing my happy dance*

*Still the friend that is upset with me isnt talkin...sadness..im scared to talk to him..ahhh

I saw chris today and his mom, ahh it was soooooooo frickin sad! I couldnt do it! He has so much on him right now. AHh its crazy!

I dont feel like writing anymore...so thats good..lata

Hey guys

Sorry i didnt write yesterday i was really busy {im sure you dont really give a crap lol, not like you read all of it anyway lol its too much to read sometimes i know! haha} I had a powder puff meaning. Stef, Sarah and I got picked to coach for the junior class cheerleading boys. Woot! Its gonna be awesome! I Also had cheer practice. So after practice I get home like 5:30 and then leave to Britts house to pick her up at like 6:30. We went shopping for a backpack but never found one. Needless to say we ended up at a toy store buying a board game..lol quija. Yeah we are such lil girls. We tried playing it cuz everyone says it works and stuff but didnt for us. We finally figured out we were doing it wrong but we didnt have to time to play. We'll have to wait til next time. I took her home and I came home did hw and stuff went to bed. OhHH yeah my Bri called me! woot! hes doing good! I was sooooo happy to hear from him! I really miss him a lot he will be back on Monday thou so yeah woot!

Today was so rushed Britt and i got to school early to do hw and such cuz we didnt finish it last nite.*innocent look*
I love Wednesdays they are awesome! It was a pretty good day. Til like 6th per. when i found out that the hurricane is coming striaght toward us and our game has been moved to 2mow and we have no school on friday. Meaning school will probably be extented to June! oh yeah..greattt. Im so over this whole hurricane crap its ruining my life!! ahh.

I had a crucible meeting today. I love it Im soo frickin excited! Everyone seems really great and Devon seems awesome {director!} Im really glad sandra made me try out! Mon Mon has been really supportive too she came up to me yesterday i think it was and told me we had a meeting shes so excited for me and that makes me real welcome cuz im new to the whole drama and play stuff. THANKs MOn!

Ive been staying after school all week! Its crazy! im not use to living at school! lol

*Him-still hasnt called me like he said he would on monday so yeah im over it. I think i may write him and note and give it to him. I know childish but i cant tell him how i feel face to face or on the phone cuz its soo hard. I dont know why either! ahh its crazy! Oh yeah and when i got home today my mom asked me to go by his house tonite to drop his mom's stuff off for her. So yeah I may see him tonite. SO idk if thats a good or bad thing? Im really scared to know..

*the friend that is upset with me. I told him i was sorry but he still isnt talking to me?! i know i was wrong but i said sorry and i didnt mean to hurt him or snap at him. i dont know what else to do! i hope he talks soon thou!

YUck im still sickish! I hate it lol! oh well

Today we had to vote for princess and prince. I didnt knwo who to vote for so i voted Alli K. and Brian C. {DUH!}

Tonite im also going to see chris {ex bf} to drop off food {the church is doing it cuz his mommy has cancer so we all thought it would be nice to kinda help out} Plus i think it would be nice to see him again, you know! I hope it goes well! Youre probably wonderin what do i mean church, yeah im not apart of the youth anymore but im still apart of our small group {which is a bunch of ppl from the church that does their own lil group things like the youth but its not kids ususally}

Well I think thats about it

the end for now...

stay safe everyone! lOVE you

HAppy labor day weekend..{hopefully it will be good ahh! no hurricane!!!}

So today sucks! I dont even want to go there. I got up sick, with a cold, I felt like crap, and I had horrible dreams all nite. 

Got to Britt's house, she felt the same lol {isnt that weird?} we probably got eachother sick. 

Right now, school is boring. I failed my physics test. Woot go me, oh well I really dont care. 

Before Drama, everything started to get better. Josh came up and scared the crap out of me. lol hes a funny kid. He made me smile. Drama was fun..with Jessica, Britt, Sandra, and ANdy! haha random conversations. Cheerleading was fine too. that was my break from everything.

Took Britt, Steph, and Kt bucket home after practice. 

My day has been up and down. UGh Im not in a good mood at all! Everyone is just pissing me off. My sister just walks in the door and just pisses me off. Idk. 

I FREAKIN MISS BRIAN! I WANT BRI BACK. *tears!

Him is frickin annoying me, cuz im really confused and Im sick of it.

One of my friends decides to be pissed off at me..when I was just tellin him he should stick up for him self for once. Instead of takin everyones crap, and he pins it on me saying I called him stupid. When that word never came out of my mouth! So whatever I didnt feel like hearing how horrible I am. So I blocked him, then unblocked him when he got off. I didnt mean for him to take it like that what I said earlier. I didnt think he would take it so literal. WHatever cant deal with it. IM just FRICKIN horrible bestfriend!!!!!!!!!! okay! so yeah make a note to yourself. Brandi isnt a good friend..

Its scary I seem to be gaining and loosing friends. Some friends Im becoming closer too, and others well..you can see..its probably me. I say too much, and Im a bitch at times, but I wouldnt hurt you but I guess Im hurtful with my words. I only saying what I think. Im sick of always being the nice one. I hate how everyone just expects me to take their side. I have my own damn opinon. I guess I just voice it too much. Oh well..

I feel trapped. It seems like everyone wants me dead. Not literally but you know, everyone wants to bring me down. I cant handle anymore. Im frickin sorry! I keep just brushing everything off and not facing it. Usually I will face it, even if its the wrong way to face it. But everything, is too much, I keep turning away.

Church well church..I talked to Leo today Im so happy cuz I miss him like crazy. My mom talked to me last nite about the youth group and I get pissed off every single time. I dont know why, I just do. I dont want to talk about it, I guess. I dont want to start over again. Im just sick oF iT! 

The end..yes im done bitching..

sorry I know lovely entry..

and oh yeah brittany is basically grounded so I cant talk to her and yeah it sickening..bc i feel kinda lost..

and ohhh yeah i triped up the stairs today and i have a lil burn on my hand from it thank god no one was in the wall way! smart one huh?

Yesterday was cool. I went and picked Britt up at like 1. We went frickin everywhere we went to winndixie to get our poster and M&Ms. Then we went to waterford. Came back. I saw him on the road lol and he called late last nite? So yeah we kinda talked..IDK its soo confusing. He really hurts my head! 

Anywho Brittany and I went to chick fila lol, um and just drove frickin everywhere. We went on great adventures. After that I dropped her home. I went picked Meg up from work. We went to waterford and saw the exorist omgosh SCARY MOvie. I mean I was covering my eyes..and I Love scary movies! It was a really good movie thou! If you hate scary movies def dont go see that! You will pee ur pants! Um after the movies we picked up our tile. Its so prettyful. I dropped meg home and I went to Stephs house to babysit and that was saturday. It was a bunch of fun. I helped Steph get ready they went to cowboys. She was looking hott! lol crazy girl! 

Today Im gonna go get Britt do project and hw..stuff around the house you know. Thats what Sundays are for.lol!

Im splitin this peice..as Jessica would say..btw Jessica my phone never rang?! 

Lata...have a good rest of the day..cuz SCHOOL 2mow! AHHHH

Well today was a good day! woot. I was so hyper. Everything is gravy again. Ive been so busy ahh. Today I stayed at school til like 5 then came back at 6. CRAZY!

So Im in T.C.{drama} at school as one of my class. Well there has been many plays and I usually cant try out from them cuz of cheerleading. 

So today was the try outs for the Crucible. I wasnt sure if I was going to try out or not because Ive never done a play before. I never was interested and it always messed with the cheer Schedule. 

Well Sandra, and Jessica said I should and I kinda wanted to. Plus other ppl were very positive and really wanted to me to try out{to my surprise?! lol}. So today I practiced in drama to them and such. After school I try outed for mary warren {I knew I wouldnt get her bc I dont really have the experience, cuz shes kinda a big part in the play, plus there are so many better ppl out there that has been in plays and such, that try outed so I wasnt expected anything} 

Needless to say when I got up there I wasnt nervous like I thought I would be. Thanks to ANDY! and Sandra cuz they went up there with me and read lines. ANDY YOURE FRICKIN AWESOME THANKS SWEETIE AND CONGRATS! I did okay, I could have done better but it was tough comp and I was scared to death.
 
I had cheerleading at 6 so I had to leave after I auditioned and I wouldnt know who go what. So Brittany called me and left a mess on my phone. I got a little part. Im one of the girls. So thats cool I didnt think I was going to get anything. Im happy about it woot. For my first try, I was proud. You all must come to the show :-D. Andy got mr. protector. woot go you! Im so proud. Sandra is one of the girls with me. Im excited this is my first play woot! 

My first varsity cheerleading game was tonite also. It was fun then it got boring after a while. Heather did an awesome basket. So proud of her. I did okay cheering wise, I didnt miss up too bad lol, at the end I kinda gave up and didnt give it my all. I was like okay whatever I wANT to Go HOME! We were all like that thou so yeah.

Today was a pretty good day. Woot Woot. School is gonna be more exciting.

OH yeah Corinne, Jessica and Scott you guys are my heros! lol thanks for coming to the game! lol I loVE it!

2mow Im babysitting at nite I think, and Im hangin with Meg, well Im suppose to be...lol

Still havent heard or seen him since tuesday..hmm...:-D

Everyone have a great weekend..

oxox
Bran
" Why are you Trying So Hard To Fit In When You Were Born To Stand Out"

Yeah so yesterday wasnt a great day. It wasnt that it was a bad day, it was just everything that has been inside that bulited up came out. All things were bugging me! I couldnt take it. I needed space from the outside world! Drama Queenish..yeah I know get over it..

Today was so much better. I looked like crap but hey whatever..lol I pulled together today! lol nothing new, I was hyper and kinda still am. I had ort. tonite so I had to wear my uniform to help ppl around the school. OMGOSH I HATE OUR UNIFORMS ahhhhH!!! oh well..Game 2mow..SO yeah have to wear it again 2mow all day. GREEEAT..oh well. So yeah our first game is 2mow you better all be there, its at Lh its free. woot! I better see you there! Wink*

Bri left today I didnt get to call him at school Tears* but he knows i Love him!

Well I havent talked to him since Tuesday but Im not worried about it cuz all I have to do now is talk to him the next time I see him. I got it all under control. I think I know what I want. We'll see!

So Chris (ex bf) called today that was random! Theres a lot going on there. I hope everything turns out okay. I feel really bad for him. I wish I could help! But he knows Im here for him. His mommy has cancer its really sad. AHh soo much sadness.

Yeah Cheer practice was good. Everything is okay. If I failed my physics test, I talked to Mr. sesus and told him I may have to get out of the class and he said that was fine but I could probably at least pull off a B or such. So idk I may stay. I like him hes not so bad after all.

For right now Im better..everything is okay...

Yesterday I just had to throw a fit...it was just one of those days..

BouNCin..

Im sorry Im not talkin or I was mean. I cant help it. 

Im so mad at everything and everyone. I cant deal with everything at once. Everything is being thrown at me. Im sick of everything being okay when its NOT! 

I cant scream, I cant yell, I cant even talk sometimes. I sit there and Im in space. Nothing effects me! When inside IM CRYIN MY FREAKIN HEART OUT. I cant breath! Im just so annoyed! I cant do this anymore.

Everything is bottled up and I cant even start because Ive just been blocking everything out. EVerything. Everything has to be sad nothing is good anymore. IM SICK OF IT..Im not this girl anymore.. WHere the hell am I? Where is me? always happy, always smiling? All I do now is bitch!

God Im sorry, Im sick of everything. There is so much bad in this world. I just want to cry, and no tears are coming out!

Okay one more thing..when I saw him again today ...I went insane..I was scared I was gonna have to give him up..if he didnt call me by saturday! ahhh I figured out that..I like him its not past feelings. I Know fickle! Its crazy. Truthfully I dont think I ever stopped caring for him! When he pulled beside me..and was a lil in front. I saw the smoke coming from his window. I was aggravated at him and as soon as I pulled up it was gone. Which was random..but I know he was smoking. He knows I know, so why does it matter?! Whatever..that kinda pissed me off! But hes fixin to be 18. So oh well. Idk. I Know I have feelings for him..and I care for him, but I dont know where I want it to go. aslkdfjaaksdfja SOO CONFUSING!

It was funny when we saw him today cuz everything was reminding me of him again. I saw all these vans that looked like his moms, ahh it wouldnt go away and then..he comes up behind me. Brittany thought I was playing..shes likes yeah laughing, and Im like NO im SERIOUS! and shes turns around and there he was. :-D

AHH IM A DORK!!! AHHHHHHHH...a STUPID DORK!..AHHHHH *sigh* cant help it.

Its like a roller coaster..Its the only thing keeping me sane..well besides my bffs! Cough BRITTANy & TIFFANy Cough 

Now Im wondering..what I should do now..I know nothing. He called thats good..so lets see if he calls again..he hates the phone. ANd he never like talks talks on the phone. So im really surprised he called Sunday after he left..{usually he will call a day or 2 later} then 2day 3 freakin times?! and leaves a message..HA..idk?!

CRAZY>>>>>

woot Bri got a job guys..go you go you! hottness..now its gonna be goin to publix instead of winndixie..uh oh..I had a lot of fun today..thanks Brittany and my cheer squad woot..sorry random add ons..

well today was boring..as usual nothing exciting TIL after school that was the best. So after cheerleading i pick brittany up we come home and do hw then we decided that we are hungry so we got get chick-fil-ia on university..okay bad idea cuz there was so much traffic but good idea bc there were guys everywhere. There are never any like hott guys that are driving usually. So we were being retarded had the music up loud and dancing and crap. We get our food and leave to home again.
